1. Configure and install Tomcat
2. Code 1 login page and 1 welcome page
3. Implement login functionality using Filter and Servlet, the successfully logged user should be redirected to the welcome page.
4. Retrieve a list of trades (ticker, price, buy/sell volume, buy/sell action, client name) from CSV file.
5. The application should be able to search a specific transaction by any field listed above.
6. Implement the same functionality using Spring Boot + Spring MVC
7. Feel free to make assumptions
8. Feel free to copy code from StackOverflow :)